git-svn的使用含svn服务器搭建

centos7服务器

一、svn服务器的搭建
参考：
https://www.cnblogs.com/-mrl/p/8980244.html
https://www.cnblogs.com/h2zZhou/p/6136948.html


yum -y install subversion
rpm -ql subversion\

mkdir /var/svnrepos
svnadmin create /var/svnrepos/repos1
cd /var/svnrepos/repos1/
vi authz
[/]：表示根目录，即 /var/svnrepos
vagrant = rw：表示用户luo对根目录具有读写权限。

vi passwd
[users]
vagrant = 123456

vi svnserve.conf
anon-access = none：表示禁止匿名用户访问。
auth-access = write：表示授权用户拥有读写权限。
password-db = passswd：指定用户名口令文件，即 passwd 文件。
authz-db = authz：指定权限配置文件，即 authz 文件。
realm = /var/svnrepos：指定认证域，即 /var/svnrepos 目录。

systemctl stop firewalld
svnserve -d -r /var/svnrepos

svn验证
ps -ef |grep 'svnserve'
svn默认端口3690
svn co svn://192.168.56.101/repos1
vi 1.txt
svn add 1.txt
svn commit -m "1 commit"

二、git-svn的安装及验证
yum install -y git-svn
yum install -y git

目录工作区
/home/vagrant/svnwork   （svn工作区）
             /gitwork    (git工作区）
             
进入到svn工作区           
cd /home/vagrant/svnwork
假设已经有了svn的代码，如
svn co svn://192.168.56.101/repos1
cd repos1
echo "1">>1.txt
svn add 1.txt
svn commit -m "svn commit 1"

切换到git工作区
cd /home/vagrant/gitwork
git svn clone svn://192.168.56.101/repos1
cd repos1
这时master已经作为git的remote上游
git checkout -b b1
echo "2">>1.txt
git add 1.txt
git commit -m "git commit 2"

切换到svn工作区
这时为了制造冲突的情况
在svn目录下
cd /home/vagrant/svnwork
cd repos1
echo "3">>1.txt
svn add 1.txt
svn commit -m "svn commit 3"

切换到git工作区
echo "4">>1.txt
git add 1.txt
git commit -m "git commit 4"
git svn rebase master
rebase后会提示冲突，解决冲突并提交，如下
vi 1.txt
git add 1.txt
git rebase --continue
git svn dcommit



mac下报过
git svn
Can't locate SVN/Core.pm in @INC (you may need to install the SVN::Core module) (@INC contains: /usr/local/Cellar/git/2.24.0/share/perl5 /Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer/Library/Perl/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level /Library/Developer/CommandLineTools/Library/Perl/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level /Library/Perl/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level /Library/Perl/5.18 /Network/Library/Perl/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level /Network/Library/Perl/5.18 /Library/Perl/Updates/5.18.4 /System/Library/Perl/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level /System/Library/Perl/5.18 /System/Library/Perl/Extras/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level /System/Library/Perl/Extras/5.18 .) at /usr/local/Cellar/git/2.24.0/share/perl5/Git/SVN/Utils.pm line 6.
BEGIN failed--compilation aborted at /usr/local/Cellar/git/2.24.0/share/perl5/Git/SVN/Utils.pm line 6.
Compilation failed in require at /usr/local/Cellar/git/2.24.0/share/perl5/Git/SVN.pm line 25.
BEGIN failed--compilation aborted at /usr/local/Cellar/git/2.24.0/share/perl5/Git/SVN.pm line 32.
Compilation failed in require at /usr/local/Cellar/git/2.24.0/libexec/git-core/git-svn line 22.
BEGIN failed--compilation aborted at /usr/local/Cellar/git/2.24.0/libexec/git-core/git-svn line 22.
通过以下解决：
xcode-select --install
sudo mkdir /Library/Perl/5.18/auto
sudo ln -s /Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer/Library/Perl/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level/SVN /Library/Perl/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level
sudo ln -s /Applications/Xcode.app/Contents/Developer/Library/Perl/5.18/darwin-thread-multi-2level/auto/SVN /Library/Perl/5.18/auto/
brew install git svn
解决了

引：https://www.cnblogs.com/mantoudev/p/8506543.html
